{"tid":741084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要表揚呢位九巴站務助理","createTime":"2018-07-13T11:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T11:40:27.000Z","uid":39878,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"029ad6764e5b48e6ef2ff204901f2df5925d8881","tid":741084,"uid":39878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"岩岩喺濱景花園去九龍既巴士站 <br />\n呢個站務助理應該係每日放工時間都喺度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/191949_1de24625e1af8bd0845746360abf4249.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F191949_1de24625e1af8bd0845746360abf4249.png&h=e7ac7e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位站務助理唔止盡責 直情係要表揚<br />\n自己成個背脊都濕晒 但係擔遮去遮住上車乘客<br />\n<br />\n但點解有d人可以連唔該都冇句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n人地職責唔包架"},{"pid":"a8019552981603ddae1424f924fa0bbdd53bef03","tid":741084,"uid":13504,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"希望每一個乘客都識得對佢講多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53692c2d14284c05a92833804760239dbf05450c","tid":741084,"uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:24:54.000Z","msg":"好慘，打份工啫，又比人擺上枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9f771c3c1dba27a5d16f5e5790075881b01ece","tid":741084,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:26:31.000Z","msg":"自己成日唔該前唔該後就比人覺得扮野野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b484a0d39a859865527b9a553b6ca5ac073ff6","tid":741084,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed9f771c3c1dba27a5d16f5e5790075881b01ece","tid":741084,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:26:31.000Z","msg":"自己成日唔該前唔該後就比人覺得扮野野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"rep